The paper deals with a network of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs) that cooperatively complete sensing tasks. This involves trajectory optimization, sensing location optimization, and UAV scheduling. The paper also proposes an iterative optimization algorithm to solve these sub-problems jointly. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The paper also deals with optimization problems related to robotics (cs.RO), networked systems (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), and information theory (cs.IT).
